video.title: Paparazzi footage of Cynthia Nixon being grumpy in the city
video.description: Cynthia Nixon arrived for a guest appearance on the Early Show, and didn't seem too happy about our camera. She was about to walk toward the camera, but quickly switched directions just as she spotted it. The camera girl says "Good morning, Cynthia!" enthusiastically, but she has no response other than to walk by with an angry look on her face. As she walks by, the camera girl says "Ok! Woke up on the wrong side of the bed. Bye bye." On the way out of the studio, Cynthia stopped to sign autographs for a few fans with little expression still. The camera girl says "Good morning, Cynthia" again, once again without any response.
